# Generated cmd.exe PE stubs (produced by `cargo run --bin dump_cmd` /
# `cargo run --bin mkcmd`). The kernel embeds them via
# `include_bytes!("../resources/pe/cmd_x86_64.exe")` at compile time,
# but the bytes themselves are rebuildable and must not be committed.
